works.description:
I sit here right now broken, sick and aching. I slept little through the night in pain and yet now that pain has turned to confusion and admittedly anger as well.



    Throughout my life i've always been a curious person who liked to look for answers. Even if its something little I want an answer. When I get bored I tend to look up random things and many times those random things turn into people I know. Back in October I got bored and began googling Terry's name thinking all it would hit would be his different sites I knew about. I was blown away when a very talented blogger had him in her blog, including a picture I've always seen as him and enjoyed looking at (hey you have to admit when a guy is built he is built).
